{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時）","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML <code>&lt;marquee&gt;</code> 元素用作插入一段文字的捲動區域。你可以透過屬性，控制文字在到達邊緣後的應對動作。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>DOM 介面</th>\n      <th><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMarqueeElement\"><code>HTMLMarqueeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"behavior\"><a id=\"attr-behavior\" href=\"#attr-behavior\"><b><code>behavior</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定文字如何在 marquee 內捲動。可用值為 <code>scroll</code>、<code>slide</code>、<code>alternate</code>。若無指定，預設值為 <code>scroll</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"bgcolor\"><a id=\"attr-bgcolor\" href=\"#attr-bgcolor\"><b><code>bgcolor</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>透過色彩名或十六進位值指定背景顏色。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"direction\"><a id=\"attr-direction\" href=\"#attr-direction\"><b><code>direction</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定 marquee 內的捲動方向。可用值為 <code>left</code>、<code>right</code>、<code>up</code>、<code>down</code>。若無指定，預設值為 <code>left</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定像素或百分比高度。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"hspace\"><a id=\"attr-hspace\" href=\"#attr-hspace\"><b><code>hspace</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定橫向外邊（horizontal margin）</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"loop\"><a id=\"attr-loop\" href=\"#attr-loop\"><b><code>loop</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定 marquee 捲動的次數。若無指定，預設值為 -1，意思是的 marquee 將持續捲動。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrollamount\"><a id=\"attr-scrollamount\" href=\"#attr-scrollamount\"><b><code>scrollamount</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>以像素為單位，設定捲動的間隔量。預設值為 6。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"scrolldelay\"><a id=\"attr-scrolldelay\" href=\"#attr-scrolldelay\"><b><code>scrolldelay</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設定每次捲動時之間間隔的毫秒。預設值為 85。請注意，除非指定了 <code>truespeed</code>，否則小於 60 的數字會被忽略，並值使用 60。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"truespeed\"><a id=\"attr-truespeed\" href=\"#attr-truespeed\"><b><code>truespeed</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code>scrolldelay</code> 預設上會忽略低於 60 的值。但如果有 <code>truespeed</code> 的話，就不會忽略此值。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"vspace\"><a id=\"attr-vspace\" href=\"#attr-vspace\"><b><code>vspace</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>以像素或百分比值設置垂直邊距。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>設置以像素或百分比值為單位的寬度。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件處理器","title":"事件處理器","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"onbounce\"><a id=\"attr-onbounce\" href=\"#attr-onbounce\"><b><code>onbounce</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>marquee 滾動到結尾時觸發。只能在 behavior 屬性設置為 <code>alternate</code> 時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onfinish\"><a id=\"attr-onfinish\" href=\"#attr-onfinish\"><b><code>onfinish</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>marquee 完成 loop 屬性的設定值時觸發。只能在 loop 屬性設為大於 0 的數字時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"onstart\"><a id=\"attr-onstart\" href=\"#attr-onstart\"><b><code>onstart</code></b></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>marquee 開始捲動時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"start\">start()</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>開始 marquee 的捲動</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"stop\">stop()</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>停止 marquee 的捲動</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from right to left<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>up<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This text will scroll from bottom to top<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>down<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>200<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>solid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>marquee</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">behavior</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>alternate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    This text will bounce\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>marquee</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/rendering.html#the-marquee-element-2","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.marquee"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.marquee","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMarqueeElement\"><code>HTMLMarqueeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"事件處理器","id":"事件處理器"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"HTML <marquee> 元素用作插入一段文字的捲動區域。你可以透過屬性，控制文字在到達邊緣後的應對動作。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<marquee>: The Marquee element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<marquee> : l'élément de fronton (obsolète)","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<marquee>: マーキー要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<marquee>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/html/element/marquee","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/html/element/marquee/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML：超文本標記語言"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/marquee","title":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時）"}],"pageTitle":"<marquee>：捲動元素（已過時） - HTML：超文本標記語言 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}